{"title":"BH RS1 Road Bike Gets More Aero Optimized","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bh-rs1-road-bike-gets-more-aero-optimized/","date":1717571542000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-1-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"BH RS1 endurance aero road bike being ridden by a group in a field.\" /></p>\n<p>While their Ultralight and Aerolight are aimed at racers, the BH RS1 takes what they’ve learned their and apply it to a bike for the rest of us.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That means aerodynamics, but also comfort. Speed, but also stability. And now, it gets a more integrated design to keep up with trends.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>BH RS1 frame and cockpit</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1466\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2.jpg\" alt=\"BH RS1 endurance aero road bike shown from side.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike uses their “Performance Carbon Layup”, which is reasonably light but emphasizes comfort over ultimate stiffness and gram shaving. It’s made with their same Hollow Core construction for perfectly smooth inner and outer tube walls, just with a different level of carbon fiber.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1466\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of BH RS1 endurance aero road bike.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-4-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The FSA ACR headset system hides all brake hoses and any wiring, etc., internally from the controls through the frame. Geometry is aimed at endurance riders, with a taller front end for a more comfortable, upright riding position. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1466\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of BH RS1 endurance aero road bike.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-3-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The aero seatpost gets a hidden wedge binder that looks sleek and puts less pressure on the post itself.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1466\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of BH RS1 endurance aero road bike.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-7-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The tubes get updated Kamm Tail shapes, and the fork is revised to fit up to 700x32mm tires while maintaining its signature look at the crown.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Other nifty features</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1466\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of BH RS1 endurance aero road bike.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-5-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The magnetic Planck rear light slots directly into the aero seatpost.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1466\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of BH RS1 endurance aero road bike.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-6-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Quick release thru axles get their Hidden Quick Lever for stealthy, tool-free wheel removal.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8.jpg\"><img width=\"2400\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8.jpg\" alt=\"BH RS1 endurance aero road bike shown from front angle.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8.jpg 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BH-RS1-aero-endurance-road-bike-2024-8-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>An 86mm wide BB368EVO bottom bracket gives it a stiff, wide frame for maximum power transmission.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Complete bikes come in four build options starting at €3,999.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.bhbikes.com/en_INT/bikes/road_performance/rs1\" target=\"_blank\">BHbikes.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bh-rs1-road-bike-gets-more-aero-optimized/\">BH RS1 Road Bike Gets More Aero Optimized</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"cde81e9176a12ad9e92022276dc5ac2d9d1153f3315178761e0a8ab9148a40c8","category":"Cycling"}